	<clause id="_the_different_phases_in_detail" obligation="normative"><title>The different phases in detail</title><clause id="_phase_1_traceability_to_the_ipk_with_additional_uncertainty_component" obligation="normative"><title>Phase 1: Traceability to the IPK, with additional uncertainty component</title><p id="_8ac1308d-fb47-4243-b2d3-ddd14ba498fb">On 20 May 2019, the reference quantity for the mass unit changes from the mass of the IPK to the fixed numerical value of the Planck constant. At that time, the uncertainty of the adjusted value of the Planck constant prior to the redefinition (1 part in 10<sup>8</sup>) will be re-assigned to the mass of the IPK, which will then have an uncertainty of <stem type="MathML"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>10</mn><mo rspace="thickmathspace">⁢</mo><mrow xref="U_ug"><mi mathvariant="normal">µg</mi></mrow>
	
	
	
	
